{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Gal|3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","chapter":3,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":1,"text":"You foolish Galatians! Who has cast a spell on you, before whose eyes Jesus Christ was publicly portrayed as crucified?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":2,"text":"I only want to learn this from you: Did you receive the Spirit by the works of the law or by believing what you heard?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":3,"text":"Are you so foolish? After beginning by the Spirit, are you now finishing by the flesh?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":4,"text":"Did you experience so much for nothing —if in fact it was for nothing?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":5,"text":"So then, does God give you the Spirit and work miracles among you by your doing the works of the law? Or is it by believing what you heard —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":6,"text":"just like Abraham who believed God, and it was credited to him for righteousness?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":7,"text":"You know, then, that those who have faith, these are Abraham’s sons.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":8,"text":"Now the Scripture saw in advance that God would justify the Gentiles by faith and proclaimed the gospel ahead of time to Abraham, saying, All the nationswill be blessed through you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":9,"text":"Consequently, those who have faith are blessed with Abraham, who had faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":10,"text":"For all who rely on the works of the law are under a curse, because it is written, Everyone who does not do everything written in the book of the law is cursed.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":11,"text":"Now it is clear that no one is justified before God by the law, because the righteous will live by faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":12,"text":"But the law is not based on faith; instead, the one who does these things will live by them.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":13,"text":"Christ redeemed us from the curse of the law by becoming a curse for us, because it is written, Cursed is everyone who is hung on a tree.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":14,"text":"The purpose was that the blessing of Abraham would come to the Gentiles by Christ Jesus, so that we could receive the promised Spirit through faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":15,"text":"Brothers and sisters, I’m using a human illustration. No one sets aside or makes additions to a validated human will.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":16,"text":"Now the promises were spoken to Abraham and to his seed. He does not say “and to seeds,” as though referring to many, but referring to one, and to your seed, who is Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":17,"text":"My point is this: The law, which came 430 years later, does not invalidate a covenant previously established by God and thus cancel the promise.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":18,"text":"For if the inheritance is based on the law, it is no longer based on the promise; but God has graciously given it to Abraham through the promise.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":19,"text":"Why, then, was the law given? It was added for the sake of transgressions until the Seed to whom the promise was made would come. The law was put into effect through angels by means of a mediator.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":20,"text":"Now a mediator is not just for one person alone, but God is one.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":21,"text":"Is the law therefore contrary to God’s promises? Absolutely not! For if the law had been granted with the ability to give life, then righteousness would certainly be on the basis of the law.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":22,"text":"But the Scripture imprisoned everything under sin’s power, so that the promise might be given on the basis of faith in Jesus Christ to those who believe.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":23,"text":"Before this faith came, we were confined under the law, imprisoned until the coming faith was revealed.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":24,"text":"The law, then, was our guardian until Christ, so that we could be justified by faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":25,"text":"But since that faith has come, we are no longer under a guardian,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":26,"text":"for through faith you are all sons of God in Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":27,"text":"For those of you who were baptized into Christ have been clothed with Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":28,"text":"There is no Jew or Greek, slave or free, male and female; since you are all one in Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","bookOrder":47,"chapter":3,"verse":29,"text":"And if you belong to Christ, then you are Abraham’s seed, heirs according to the promise.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Gal","chapter":3,"paragraphStarts":[1,7,10,15,19,27],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Justification through Faith"},{"beforeVerse":10,"text":"Law and Promise"},{"beforeVerse":19,"text":"The Purpose of the Law"},{"beforeVerse":27,"text":"Sons and Heirs"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You foolish "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:14","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Galatians! Who has cast a spell on you, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add not to obey the truth"},{"kind":"text","text":" before whose eyes Jesus Christ was publicly portrayed "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add among you"},{"kind":"text","text":" as crucified? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 27:22","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 1:14","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":14},{"label":"Mt 27:22","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add not to obey the truth"},{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss add among you"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I only want to learn this from you: Did you receive the Spirit by the works of the law or by believing what you heard? "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit hearing with faith, also in v. 5"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit hearing with faith, also in v. 5"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Are you so foolish? After beginning by the Spirit, are you now finishing by the flesh? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Did you experience "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Or suffer"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:29","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" so much for nothing —if in fact it was for nothing? "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 1:29","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[{"marker":4,"text":"Or suffer"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So then, does God give you the Spirit and work miracles "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" among you by your doing the works of the law? Or is it by believing what you heard — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 13:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"just like Abraham who believed God,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 14:1","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and it was credited to him for righteousness? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 15:6","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 15:6","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":6,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 14:1","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":1},{"label":"Gn 15:6","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":6},{"label":"Gn 15:6","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You know, then, that those who have faith, these are Abraham’s sons. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:37","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":39,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 8:37","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":37},{"label":"Jn 8:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":39}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now the Scripture saw in advance that God would justify the Gentiles by faith and proclaimed the gospel ahead of time to Abraham, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 16:15","book":"Gen","chapter":16,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:37","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":37,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:16","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" saying, All the nations"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or Gentiles"},{"kind":"text","text":"will be blessed through you."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 12:3","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 18:18","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 12:3","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 18:18","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 16:15","book":"Gen","chapter":16,"verse":15},{"label":"Jn 8:37","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":37},{"label":"Heb 2:16","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":16},{"label":"Gn 12:3","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":3},{"label":"Gn 18:18","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":18},{"label":"Gn 12:3","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":3},{"label":"Gn 18:18","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or Gentiles"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Consequently, those who have faith are blessed with Abraham, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":39,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" who had faith. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or with believing Abraham"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 8:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":39}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or with believing Abraham"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For all who rely on the works of the law are under a curse, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:10","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" because it is written, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:15","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Everyone who does not do everything written in the book of the law is cursed."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 27:26","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":26,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 27:26","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":26,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:15","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":15,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jms 3:10","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"Ac 15:15","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":15},{"label":"Dt 27:26","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":26},{"label":"Dt 27:26","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":26},{"label":"Rm 4:15","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now it is clear that no one is justified before God by the law, because the righteous will live"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:21","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" by faith."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hab 2:4","book":"Hab","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hab 2:4","book":"Hab","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 1:21","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":21},{"label":"Hab 2:4","book":"Hab","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Hab 2:4","book":"Hab","chapter":2,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the law is not based on faith; instead, the one who does these things will live by them."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:5","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:5","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:5","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":5},{"label":"Lv 18:5","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Christ redeemed us from the curse of the law by becoming a curse for us, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:24","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" because it is written, Cursed is everyone who is hung on a tree."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 21:23","book":"Deu","chapter":21,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 21:23","book":"Deu","chapter":21,"verse":23,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:30","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":30,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Pt 2:24","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":24},{"label":"Dt 21:23","book":"Deu","chapter":21,"verse":23},{"label":"Dt 21:23","book":"Deu","chapter":21,"verse":23},{"label":"Ac 5:30","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":30}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The purpose was that the blessing of Abraham would come to the Gentiles by Christ Jesus, so that we could receive the promised Spirit through faith. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:16","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":16,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 4:16","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Brothers and sisters, I’m using a human illustration. No one sets aside or makes additions to a validated human will. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or a human covenant that has been ratified"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or a human covenant that has been ratified"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now the promises were spoken to Abraham and to his seed. He does not say “and to seeds,” as though referring to many, but referring to one, and to your seed,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 12:7","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 13:15","book":"Gen","chapter":13,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 17:8","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 24:7","book":"Gen","chapter":24,"verse":7,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 12:7","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 13:15","book":"Gen","chapter":13,"verse":15,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 17:8","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":8,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 24:7","book":"Gen","chapter":24,"verse":7,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" who is Christ. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 12:7","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":7},{"label":"Gn 13:15","book":"Gen","chapter":13,"verse":15},{"label":"Gn 17:8","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":8},{"label":"Gn 24:7","book":"Gen","chapter":24,"verse":7},{"label":"Gn 12:7","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":7},{"label":"Gn 13:15","book":"Gen","chapter":13,"verse":15},{"label":"Gn 17:8","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":8},{"label":"Gn 24:7","book":"Gen","chapter":24,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"My point is this: The law, which came 430 years later, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 15:13","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:40","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":40,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:6","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" does not invalidate a covenant previously established by God "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add in Christ"},{"kind":"text","text":" and thus cancel the promise. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 15:13","book":"Gen","chapter":15,"verse":13},{"label":"Ex 12:40","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":40},{"label":"Ac 7:6","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss add in Christ"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For if the inheritance is based on the law, it is no longer based on the promise; but God has graciously given it to Abraham through the promise."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Why, then, was the law given? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:15","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 5:20","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" It was added for the sake of transgressions "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or because of transgressions"},{"kind":"text","text":" until the Seed to whom the promise was made would come. The law was put into effect through angels "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 16:7","book":"Gen","chapter":16,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:49","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":49,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:11","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:19","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":19,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 14:6","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":6,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" by means of a mediator. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:6","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":6,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 4:15","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":15},{"label":"Rm 5:20","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":20},{"label":"Gn 16:7","book":"Gen","chapter":16,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 13:49","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":49},{"label":"Lk 1:11","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 5:19","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":19},{"label":"Rv 14:6","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":6},{"label":"Heb 8:6","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or because of transgressions"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now a mediator is not just for one person alone, but God is one. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 6:4","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 6:4","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Is the law therefore contrary to God’s promises? Absolutely not! For if the law had been granted with the ability to give life, then righteousness would certainly be on the basis of the law. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the Scripture imprisoned everything under sin’s power, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit under sin"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 6:23","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that the promise might be given on the basis of faith "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:22","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Jesus Christ to those who believe. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 11:24","book":"Mrk","chapter":11,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:43","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":43,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:9","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 6:23","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":23},{"label":"Rm 3:22","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":22},{"label":"Mk 11:24","book":"Mrk","chapter":11,"verse":24},{"label":"Jn 3:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 10:43","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":43},{"label":"Rm 10:9","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":9},{"label":"1Pt 1:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit under sin"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Before this faith "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" came, we were confined under the law, imprisoned until the coming faith was revealed. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:21","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Lk 10:21","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The law, then, was our guardian until Christ, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:17","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:17","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:10","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that we could be justified by faith. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:17","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":17},{"label":"Col 2:17","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":17},{"label":"Heb 9:10","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But since that faith "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" has come, we are no longer under a guardian, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"for through faith you are all sons of God in Christ Jesus."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For those of you who were baptized into Christ have been clothed with Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 31:25","book":"Pro","chapter":31,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 31:25","book":"Pro","chapter":31,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There is no Jew or Greek, slave or free, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:33","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":33,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" male and female; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:12","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 12:13","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:6","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" since you are all one "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:11","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Christ Jesus. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 8:33","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":33},{"label":"Rm 10:12","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":12},{"label":"1Co 12:13","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":13},{"label":"Gl 5:6","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":6},{"label":"Jn 17:11","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gal:3:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And if you belong to Christ, then you are Abraham’s seed, heirs "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:14","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:17","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to the promise. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:13","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":13,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 4:14","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 8:17","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":17},{"label":"Rm 4:13","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279665735}